00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.042
Israel's military launched a

00:00:01.042 --> 00:00:02.335
new wave of airstrikes

00:00:02.335 --> 00:00:04.295
on the region Thursday morning.

00:00:04.295 --> 00:00:05.130
The Palestinian health

00:00:05.130 --> 00:00:06.923
ministry says more than 1200

00:00:06.923 --> 00:00:07.799
people have been killed

00:00:07.799 --> 00:00:08.925
and at least 6000

00:00:08.925 --> 00:00:10.927
wounded by Israeli bombardment.

00:00:10.927 --> 00:00:12.178
The health ministry says

00:00:12.178 --> 00:00:13.972
it expects hospitals to run out of fuel

00:00:13.972 --> 00:00:15.849
for generators today,

00:00:15.849 --> 00:00:16.891
leading to what it calls

00:00:16.891 --> 00:00:18.935
catastrophic conditions.

00:00:18.935 --> 00:00:21.938
