00:00:28.153 --> 00:00:29.696
to speak to us.

00:00:29.696 --> 00:00:30.905
I know that yesterday

00:00:30.905 --> 00:00:31.698
or certainly earlier

00:00:31.698 --> 00:00:32.949
this week, Oxfam was

00:00:32.949 --> 00:00:34.451
warning that what's happening in

00:00:34.451 --> 00:00:35.285
Gaza would lead to

00:00:35.285 --> 00:00:36.745
a humanitarian catastrophe.

00:00:36.745 --> 00:00:40.999
Would you say that's already begun?

00:00:41.082 --> 00:00:41.624
Yes. Hi.

00:00:41.624 --> 00:00:43.752
Thanks for having me, first of all.

00:00:43.752 --> 00:00:45.253
Yeah.

00:00:45.253 --> 00:00:46.087
