00:00:49.090 --> 00:00:52.385
and there is a severe,

00:00:52.469 --> 00:00:53.720
severe impact on

00:00:53.720 --> 00:00:55.096
on the population of Gaza.

00:00:55.096 --> 00:00:57.057
The entire population of Gaza.

00:00:57.057 --> 00:00:59.768
The numbers of of displaced

00:00:59.768 --> 00:01:01.561
people has been increasing,

00:01:01.561 --> 00:01:03.730
reaching to around 200

00:01:03.730 --> 00:01:06.024
