00:01:16.117 --> 00:01:18.828
We are extremely worried

00:01:18.828 --> 00:01:20.663
because of the tightening

00:01:20.663 --> 00:01:21.956
of the Israeli siege.

00:01:21.956 --> 00:01:23.083
We have to be aware

00:01:23.083 --> 00:01:24.667
that the Israeli siege

00:01:24.667 --> 00:01:27.128
